text: Nabiyow too Nabii Zakariyyaa kee maryamak kol maaqne xaagi Qellitte xaagittek Wacyih kol oobisnaama Atu maryam yahuud mixigwa iyyi keenik tet yaynabee Axcuk sinni kalooma Saami caxxah Qambisen waqdi atu ken xaqul masuginnito, usun tet maynubul itta ween waqdi Atu ken xaqul masuginnito Nabiyow
